bAiEYxTxVpKqrJPdSv-i_4BdrmD4g" style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: un=
derline;">SoftBank led a $20 million investment</a> for 30% of Alibaba. As =
I wrote in <em><a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVkEluxCAQRU_T=
7NpiMB4WLLLJNRCYajeyAQeKRL59SFtKFAmoxVfx9N9iENaUT3WkguTn0XgeoCJ8lR0QIZNaIGv=
